100
00:04:43,870 --> 00:04:44,560
I'm sorry.

101
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,950
This time I was too anxious.

102
00:04:47,630 --> 00:04:48,870
You forget me.

103
00:04:49,430 --> 00:04:50,430
