110
00:05:14,390 --> 00:05:15,560
I'm moving out tomorrow.

111
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,800
I'm going home.

112
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,240
I don't want to see him again.

113
00:05:29,270 --> 00:05:31,600
Isn't trust the most important thing
