166
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,200
I'm sorry, Meng.

167
00:08:43,030 --> 00:08:44,510
I, Xiao Hongye, swear,

168
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:46,000
from now on

169
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:48,440
